des: Hello and welcome to the Precious Puppies Club! Your birthday is coming up soon! We didn’t forget about the special date. And you know what that means? You get a gift. Wanna know what that gift is? It’s a cute, little puppy! That’s right. You get to pick a puppy, and it’s all yours to love and play with. So, it’s time to pick your dream puppy.
